/**********************  How to start this program   *******************************/

1. Now you are in the directory: :~/xiaosha/Knapsack.
2. And there are 2 folders:
	bin - stores all .class files
	src - stores all .java source codes
	
3. Then you can go into class file "/bin" and type in this command to run the program(App.java is the main class):
			cd bin
			java App
			
4. Then you could test it following the prompts.

/************************  After starting the program  ****************************/

Now you could enter in any testing data you would like to try.
Please note that the format of inputs is exactly like the examples.
After which you could choose the number of threads you would like to test(1/2/4/8).
